lead_paragraph: Sophina DeJesus won't be on the floor when Olympic gymnastics begins this weekend. Her career likely ended in April when she wrapped up her senior year at UCLA by helping the Bruins to a fifth-place finish at the NCAA championships.

headline.print_headline: As the Olympics Loom, the Gymnastics Party May Be in College
